      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont feel like i'm fighting. that's the thing. there's no core left. it's just like... a ghost haunting its own life. i look in the mirror and i see a stranger, and honestly? i feel like i'm just taking up space that could be used by someone who actually has a soul left in them. it feels so pointless to just keep existing like this.",
